&lt;p data-start=&quot;751&quot; data-end=&quot;1053&quot;&gt;This is an opportunity to design, build, test, and commission automated manufacturing equipment that directly supports Rangeview’s production ramp. You will work on real factory equipment, not theoretical process work, and your designs will impact throughput, quality, safety, and production readiness.&lt;/p&gt;
