&lt;p data-start=&quot;782&quot; data-end=&quot;1115&quot;&gt;This is an opportunity to get hands-on experience inside a modern manufacturing environment and support the daily factory, logistics, and production operations that keep Rangeview moving. You will work directly with automated equipment, materials, production processes, and cross-functional teams in a high-growth industrial setting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1117&quot; data-end=&quot;1459&quot;&gt;This role is a strong fit for someone who is detail-oriented, safety-minded, eager to learn, and interested in building a career in advanced manufacturing. You will gain exposure to equipment operation, process execution, material handling, documentation, and continuous improvement while helping support safe operations and on-time delivery.&lt;/p&gt;
