&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;You will work closely with Production, Engineering, Operations, and Finance to help keep critical materials, equipment, tooling, consumables, and services moving so the business can execute. This role is a strong fit for someone who likes practical problem solving, cross-functional work, and the chance to build scalable processes in a high-accountability environment.&lt;/p&gt;
